text.text: As a visitor and a desire to explore different styles of worship, I visited the church of Pentecost Singapore and had a spirited experience. I was warmly welcomed and found the atmosphere to be inviting and inclusive. The sermon was thought-provoking and delivered with fervor, rightly dividing the word of truth. The services were ran with professionalism and excellence. If you are visiting, transiting through Singapore or seeking a vibrant and spiritually enriching church experience I would highly recommend the Church of Pentecost- Singapore.
